text: Loretta Németh (born 9 December 1995) is a Hungarian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Hungary women's national team. ==Career== Németh has been capped for the Hungary national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian women's footballers Category:Hungary women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
